; UI — "brand" at top (studio name) + "licensed" block below (small
; legal-style text). Theme slot `Neutral` keeps both a soft grey on
; black, evoking the stock PS1 boot logo's SCEE text without copying
; its wording.
[node name="BrandCanvas" type="Node" parent="." unique_id=9100000050]
script = ExtResource("8_uican")
CanvasName = "brand"
VisibleOnLoad = true
SortOrder = 10
